{"tid":867044,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"香港讀文科 vs 外國讀文科的分別","createTime":"2018-10-18T10:43:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T09:18:57.000Z","uid":149978,"like":8,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"446b28ec6c609755ad3c1960f559cb6629428e48","tid":867044,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T10:43:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20170828-notes-from-art-to-science/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20170828-notes-from-art-to-science%2F&d=48Q0sfUiPCFtPlwj4gyWop7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=0a903ebe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20170828-notes-from-art-to-science/</a><br />\n<br />\n在香港，理科可以自由轉文科。文科<strong>不能</strong>轉讀理科，也不能讀工科。<br />\n<br />\n在外國，無論文科定理科，都可以自由轉科。文科可以轉讀理科。<br />\n<br />\n上文所講的女仔，佢高中已是文科，一直讀到大學，連宇宙的基本知識都不懂。但偶然聽到一個宇宙的talk，才知宇宙的偉大，突然對理科感興趣，毅然轉理科，並成功投考理科的博士PhD研究課程，而且間大學的知名度也于錯。<br />\n<br />\n香港的大學，想文轉理，一定死硬，封晒你後路。<br />\n<br />\n一日文科，一世文科。"},{"pid":"c20d35e9fc7ed1a17fc8f310e3bf6319a61c330a","tid":867044,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T10:53:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20170828-notes-from-art-to-science/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20170828-notes-from-art-to-science%2F&d=48Q0sfUiPCFtPlwj4gyWop7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=0a903ebe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20170828-notes-from-art-to-science/</a><br />\n<br />\n在香港，理科可以自由轉文科。文科<strong>不能</strong>轉讀理科，也不能讀工科。<br />\n<br />\n在外國，無論文科定理科，都可以自由轉科。文科可以轉讀理科。<br />\n<br />\n上文所講的女仔，佢高中已是文科，一直讀到大學，連宇宙的基本知識都不懂。但偶然聽到一個宇宙的talk，才知宇宙的偉大，突然對理科感興趣，毅然轉理科，並成功投考理科的博士PhD研究課程，而且間大學的知名度也<strong>不</strong>錯。<br />\n<br />\n香港的大學，想文轉理，一定死硬，封晒你後路。<br />\n<br />\n一日文科，一世文科。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"9d4f04bc2370e7944f0980510dd4493dfeee478c","tid":867044,"uid":215675,"like":18,"dislike":4,"scor